# graphify — graph.json/GRAPH_REPORT.md/memory/reflections ARE committed
# (see below) so a fresh clone on any laptop has the full graph + all
# accumulated session knowledge immediately, without waiting for a first
# commit there to trigger the rebuild hook. Only the per-file extraction
# cache is ignored — pure performance optimization, safe to lose, not
# useful to read.
graphify-out/cache/